dct_title_s: Minor Civil Divisions Dane County, Wisconsin 1996
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents Minor Civil Divisions (also known as Municipalities such as towns, villages, and cities) for Dane County, Wisconsin in 1996. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County and Information Office in 1996 as Coverage format. AGSL Staff converted to shapefile and simplified the data for ease of use.
